#. <section class="sutta" id="sn54.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn54.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 54"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 54"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Ekadhammavagga"
msgstr "1. One Thing"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn54.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Dutiyaphalasutta"
msgstr "5. Fruits (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.5:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ānāpānassati, bhikkhave, bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti mahānisaṃsā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when mindfulness of breathing is developed and cultivated it’s "
"very fruitful and beneficial."

msgctxt "sn54.5:1.2"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvitā ca, bhikkhave, ānāpānassati kathaṃ bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti "
"mahānisaṃsā?"
msgstr ""
"And how is mindfulness of breathing developed and cultivated to be very "
"fruitful and beneficial?"

msgctxt "sn54.5:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu araññagato vā rukkhamūlagato vā suññāgāragato vā "
"nisīdati pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ "
"upaṭṭhapetvā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant has gone to a wilderness, or to the root of a tree, or "
"to an empty hut. They sit down cross-legged, with their body straight, and "
"establish mindfulness right there."

msgctxt "sn54.5:1.4"
msgid "So satova assasati, satova passasati … pe …"
msgstr "Just mindful, they breathe in. Mindful, they breathe out. …"

msgctxt "sn54.5:1.5"
msgid ""
"‘paṭinissaggānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘paṭinissaggānupassī "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati."
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in observing letting go.’ They "
"practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out observing letting go.’"

msgctxt "sn54.5:1.6"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvitā kho, bhikkhave, ānāpānassati evaṃ bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti "
"mahānisaṃsā."
msgstr ""
"Mindfulness of breathing, when developed and cultivated in this way, is very "
"fruitful and beneficial."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.5:2.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvitāya kho, bhikkhave, ānāpānassatiyā evaṃ bahulīkatāya satta phalā "
"sattānisaṃsā pāṭikaṅkhā."
msgstr ""
"When mindfulness of breathing is developed and cultivated in this way you "
"can expect seven fruits and benefits."

msgctxt "sn54.5:2.2"
msgid "Katame satta phalā sattānisaṃsā?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "sn54.5:2.3"
msgid "Diṭṭheva dhamme paṭikacca aññaṃ ārādheti;"
msgstr "You attain enlightenment early on in this very life."

msgctxt "sn54.5:2.4"
msgid "no ce diṭṭheva dhamme paṭikacca aññaṃ ārādheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.5:2.5"
msgid "Atha maraṇakāle aññaṃ ārādheti;"
msgstr "If not, you attain enlightenment at the time of death."

msgctxt "sn54.5:2.6"
msgid ""
"no ce diṭṭheva dhamme paṭikacca aññaṃ ārādheti, no ce maraṇakāle aññaṃ "
"ārādheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.5:2.7"
msgid ""
"Atha pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā antarāparinibbāyī hoti "
"…"
msgstr ""
"If not, with the ending of the five lower fetters you’re extinguished in "
"between one life and the next …"

msgctxt "sn54.5:2.8"
msgid "upahaccaparinibbāyī hoti …"
msgstr "you’re extinguished upon landing …"

msgctxt "sn54.5:2.9"
msgid "asaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti …"
msgstr "you’re extinguished without extra effort …"

msgctxt "sn54.5:2.10"
msgid "sasaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti …"
msgstr "you’re extinguished with extra effort …"

msgctxt "sn54.5:2.11"
msgid "uddhaṃsoto hoti akaniṭṭhagāmī—"
msgstr "you head upstream, going to the Akaniṭṭha realm …"

msgctxt "sn54.5:2.12"
msgid ""
"evaṃ bhāvitāya kho, bhikkhave, ānāpānassatiyā evaṃ bahulīkatāya ime satta "
"phalā sattānisaṃsā pāṭikaṅkhā”ti."
msgstr ""
"When mindfulness of breathing is developed and cultivated in this way you "
"can expect these seven fruits and benefits.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn54.5:2.13"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
